{"tid":2069716,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★財困危機！環聯：近八成受訪者憂慮找數難","createTime":"2020-06-18T15:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T06:04:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"878c43ba7b3427828afa4cbd438c45d5a932034d","tid":2069716,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"環聯發布新一期《全球新冠肺炎疫情下消費者財政困難研究報告》，顯示疫情下，家庭收入受影響的消費者對財困憂慮回升，45%財政受影響的受訪者表示，可能在未來1至3個月內難以繳付帳單，較5月初增加5個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n研究顯示，相較於上期5月初進行的調查，受疫情影響其家庭收入的消費者由67%增加至75%，增幅達8個百分點。另外，78%受影響的受訪者對繳付帳單表示憂慮，較5月初增加15個百分點。他們表示最難以負擔的是信用卡貸款，其次為租金、保費、私人貸款及樓宇按揭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200618/bkn-20200618213012980-0618_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200618%2Fbkn-20200618213012980-0618_00842_001.html&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHmbkIIQgOyZVEIOEDwMYbAQ%3D&h=74c37ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200618/bkn-20200618213012980-0618_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"19024b77c5e11876f3c17091d5c4b69be55c6896","tid":2069716,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fb6fe7ccad49c2ccc5757a1bd7b0c6e0ac2619","tid":2069716,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}